  heroTitle="Medical Translation"
  heroSubtitle="Healthcare & Clinical Documents"
  heroIntro="Medical translation carries responsibility—accuracy can affect patient safety, treatment decisions, and professional licensing. Our <a href='/industries/healthcare/'>medical translators</a> combine language expertise with healthcare backgrounds, ensuring your medical documents communicate with the precision that clinical settings demand."
